snippet: Donald Levine, the Hasbro executive credited as the father of G.I. Joe for developing the world's first action figure, has died. He was 86....

headline.print_headline: Levine, Hasbro Exec Who Helped Create GI Joe, Dies
headline.main: Levine, Hasbro Exec Who Helped Create GI Joe, Dies

lead_paragraph: Donald Levine, the Hasbro executive credited as the father of G.I. Joe for developing the world's first action figure, has died. He was 86.
